z.com%2F%3Frbid%3D1497&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=1ff883cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://articles.zkiz.com/?rbid=1497</a><br />\n股評人鄧聲興背妻玩妹"},{"pid":"2861cd52251cc2239c43e57e46a93589a4bc01d6","tid":1278594,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:22:59.000Z","msg":"有良知既香港人"},{"pid":"7b0a5efbaa091e6a43c765336eb3c80f30b42d01","tid":1278594,"uid":51566,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:23:51.000Z","msg":"范巧茹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"988f7c873c893eed05f16f612f49d849f01e4857","tid":1278594,"uid":153458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:35:33.000Z","msg":"果然有良心嘅都唔會留喺CCTVB"},{"pid":"dae5fcaa51ec795b50532d7c12d277f756ce2173","tid":1278594,"uid":62935,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:40:45.000Z","msg":"以前睇呢條柒頭係電視答阿婆 聽日唔係升就係跌...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家撈撈下竟然撈到會長..."}]}